OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1778861472
OL,3,CTeachers raise 'serious concerns' with
OL,4,CJersey Government in leaked letter
OL,6,FVulnerable children and young people
OL,7,Fin Jersey face "clear and avoidable
OL,8,Frisks" from delays to mental health
OL,9,Fsupport, according to a group of 18
OL,10,Fteachers.
OL,12,FIn a letter sent to the Education
OL,13,FDepartment and obtained by ITV
OL,14,FChannel, they raise "serious concerns"
OL,15,Fover the current process, which they
OL,16,Fbelieve shifts the responsibility onto
OL,17,Fthem without the necessary support.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
