OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1778861472
OL,3,CTeachers raise 'serious concerns' with
OL,4,CJersey Government in leaked letter
OL,6,FThey write: "Schools are no longer
OL,7,Fsimply referring children for
OL,8,Fspecialist assessment; SENCos (Special
OL,9,FEducational Needs Coordinators) are
OL,10,Fnow expected to coordinate, evidence,
OL,11,Fadminister, and effectively gatekeep
OL,12,Faccess to specialist health services.
OL,14,F"This goes far beyond collaborative
OL,15,Fworking and represents a significant
OL,16,Fshift of clinical and administrative
OL,17,Fresponsibility into education, without
OL,18,Fmandate, funding, or agreement."
OL,26,@pD@_pmqD@_pn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1778861472
OL,3,CTeachers raise 'serious concerns' with
OL,4,CJersey Government in leaked letter
OL,6,FThe teachers say it "places excessive
OL,7,Fand unmanageable demands" on school
OL,8,Fstaff, alongside "safeguarding
OL,9,Fconcerns" as they are not "case
OL,10,Fmanagers or clinical coordinators".
OL,12,FThey state the current backlog "means
OL,13,Fsome children may wait close to two
OL,14,Fyears from initial concern to
OL,15,Fassessment," and early reports may be
OL,16,Fout of date by the time they are
OL,17,Ffinally seen.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1778861472
OL,3,CTeachers raise 'serious concerns' with
OL,4,CJersey Government in leaked letter
OL,6,FThe letter outlines that prolonged
OL,7,Fdelays can cause many issues,
OL,8,Fincluding school anxiety and a higher
OL,9,Frisk of exclusion.
OL,11,FThe teachers add: "We are also deeply
OL,12,Fconcerned by repeated instances in
OL,13,Fwhich families have reportedly been
OL,14,Finformed that schools failed to submit
OL,15,Frequired documents, leading to
OL,16,Freferrals being closed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1778861472
OL,3,CTeachers raise 'serious concerns' with
OL,4,CJersey Government in leaked letter
OL,6,F"Across schools, there have been
OL,7,Fexamples where this was not the case.
OL,8,FSituations such as these risk damaging
OL,9,Fthe trust and relationships schools
OL,10,Fwork extremely hard to build with
OL,11,Ffamilies."
OL,13,FIn conclusion, they say: "Several
OL,14,Faspects of the process appear
OL,15,Foperationally flawed.
OL,17,F"As SENCoS, we do not believe this
OL,18,Fprocess is workable or sustainable in
OL,19,Fits current form."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1778861472
OL,3,CTeachers raise 'serious concerns' with
OL,4,CJersey Government in leaked letter
OL,6,FThey are calling for proper support
OL,7,Fand resourcing, as well as an urgent
OL,8,Freview - working with schools to find
OL,9,Fa way forward.
OL,11,FIn response, the Education Department
OL,12,Ftold ITV Channel: "The Department
OL,13,Ftakes the matters raised in the letter
OL,14,Fseriously and will be looking
OL,15,Fcarefully at the concerns outlined,
OL,16,Fincluding speaking directly with staff
OL,17,Fto better understand their experiences
OL,18,Fand any issues identified.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1778861472
OL,3,CTeachers raise 'serious concerns' with
OL,4,CJersey Government in leaked letter
OL,6,F"We would like to reassure parents,
OL,7,Fcarers, and students that the
OL,8,Fsafeguarding and wellbeing of children
OL,9,Fand young people remain the absolute
OL,10,Fpriority for the Department, and it is
OL,11,Fimportant that any concerns raised are
OL,12,Fproperly considered.
OL,14,F"As this issue is ongoing, it would
OL,15,Fnot be appropriate to comment further
OL,16,Fat this stage."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
