FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1778861472
OL,3,CTeachers raise 'serious concerns' with
OL,4,CJersey Government in leaked letter
OL,6,FSeparately, ITV Channel has seen an
OL,7,Femail from Jersey's Child and
OL,8,FAdolescent Mental Health Service
OL,9,F(CAHMS) stating that it cannot
OL,10,Fcurrently help anyone else who needs
OL,11,FADHD medication, unless they are
OL,12,Falready being treated.
OL,14,FIt says: "At present, our ADHD
OL,15,Ftreatment pathway is operating at full
OL,16,Fcapacity.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1778861472
OL,3,CTeachers raise 'serious concerns' with
OL,4,CJersey Government in leaked letter
OL,6,F"In order to maintain safe practice
OL,7,Fand ensure that all children and young
OL,8,Fpeople already under our care receive
OL,9,Fmedication reviews within recommended
OL,10,Ftimescales, we are currently unable to
OL,11,Faccept any new requests for starting
OL,12,FADHD medication.
OL,14,F"We recognise that this may be
OL,15,Fdisappointing and appreciate your
OL,16,Funderstanding while we work to restore
OL,17,Fcapacity."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
